<Values version="2.0">
  <value name="xml">This is an automatic email. PLEASE DO NOT REPLY!
==================================================

An error ocurred while attempting to deliver the compliance check results to ExpressLink. The support team has been notified.

Please manually enter the information below inside ExpressLink:

CUSTOMER:
=======================================================================================
CustomerType: 		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/CustomerType%
PartyType: 		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/PartyType%
BusinessName:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/BusinessName%
FirstName:              %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/FirstName%
MiddleName:             %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/MiddleName%
LastName:               %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/LastName%
AddressLine1: 		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/AddressLine1%
AddressLine2:           %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/AddressLine2%
AddressLine3:           %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/AddressLine3%
AddressLine4:           %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/AddressLine4%
City:			%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/City%
State:			%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/State%
Zip:			%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/Zip%
SSN / TIN:              %ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/SSNTIN%


APPLICATION:
=======================================================================================
ApplicationNumber:	%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Identification/ApplicationNumber%


COMPLIANCE RESULTS:
=======================================================================================
RegOPassFail:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/RegOPassFail%
RegWPassFail:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/RegWPassFail%
PA326PassFail:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/PA326PassFail%
OFACPassFail:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/OFACPassFail%
HotFilePassFail:	%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/HotFilePassFail%
FAPassFail:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheck/FAPassFail%


ERRORS:
=======================================================================================
  ErrorType: 		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Errors[0]/Error/ErrorType%
  ErrorCode:		%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Errors[0]/Error/ErrorCode%
  ErrorDescription:	%ComplianceCheckReply/ComplianceCheckReply/Errors[0]/Error/ErrorDescription%</value>
  <record name="type" javaclass="com.wm.util.Values">
    <value name="node_type">unknown</value>
    <value name="field_name">mailBody</value>
    <value name="field_type">string</value>
    <value name="field_dim">0</value>
    <value name="nillable">true</value>
  </record>
</Values>
</DATA>
</MAPSET>
</MAP>
